    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready to work, this vehicle offers straightforward value for anyone seeking affordable transportation without the premium price tag. It shows visible wear consistent with age and use, but it remains a practical choice for commuting, errands, or a dependable backup vehicle. A smart opportunity for buyers who prioritize utility, accessibility, and honest pricing.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels that still has plenty to offer? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it starts, drives, and gives someone a great chance to get on the road without spending a fortune. A solid budget-friendly option for a commuter, first-time driver, or anyone who doesn\u2019t mind a little character. Priced fairly and represented honestly by a seller who believes in straightforward deals.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project or budget driver with honest wear and plenty of upside. Starts, runs, and delivers the kind of mechanical simplicity enthusiasts appreciate, with a drivetrain that feels fundamentally serviceable and a chassis that\u2019s a good candidate for continued use, light restoration, or weekend tinkering. Cosmetics show age and it\u2019s not a showroom car, but for someone who values usable bones over polish, this is an affordable way into a capable platform. Priced to move for the right buyer who knows what they\u2019re looking at.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Honest used car with wear, but ready for the next owner. Priced to move fast at $7,900.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A car with grit, presence, and plenty of story left to tell. This is the kind of ride that speaks to someone who sees possibility instead of polish\u2014perfect as an affordable runaround, a hands-on project, or a practical spare to keep in the driveway. It has that honest, lived-in character that gives it personality, and for the right buyer, there\u2019s real value in its simple purpose and potential. If you want something inexpensive with spirit and usefulness, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 6495.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers straightforward transportation at an accessible price. Best suited for a buyer who values affordability and sees the opportunity in a solid, usable car with plenty of life left to give. A practical choice for commuting, a backup vehicle, or a project-minded owner looking for strong value.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left for the right person? This one isn\u2019t a showroom car, but it\u2019s a straightforward, budget-friendly option for someone who wants basic transportation, a project, or a handy spare vehicle. Priced to reflect its condition, and still has the kind of character that makes a car worth a look. If you\u2019re realistic and want something inexpensive without the sales pitch, come check it out.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Solid project or budget driver with the right enthusiast bones. This car presents as a mechanically honest example with a responsive powertrain, composed road manners, and the kind of straightforward, serviceable setup that makes it appealing for someone who wants an affordable platform to sort and enjoy. It shows age and needs cosmetic/detail attention, but it still offers good core value with usable drivetrain performance, predictable steering feel, and plenty of upside for the next owner. If you want a cheap entry point into something with character and potential, this is a compelling buy.",
      "price": 7900.0,
